Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajin Sato is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't have any good news today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I was forced to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to use force to give\Nthis country a chance for the fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him resurrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,use the opportunity and ensure victory. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This old man isn't human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everyone watch. We are fighting against humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you betting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have found the whereabouts of Nagai Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest till todays autopsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,specimen 003, Nagai Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! We won't have another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He drastically differs from Hatter or Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's next? \NWhere are we running to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done running. Let's stop Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. For you to meet me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouhai must always show respect to his senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If they already decided on my \Npunishment then spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be forced to quit ajin research department, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect? \NFirst you let the Hatter do as he wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you let Nagai and Nakano escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell is awaiting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the situation changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They've decided to give you a thread to hang onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatter has made his second statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, I have decided\N to start the second wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of looking for a compromise\Nhumans chose to oppress demi-humans even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So the theme of the second wave will be cleansing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the information that Tanaka-kun\Ngot while being imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we've made a list of fifteen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If the government doesn't agree to our demands
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll kill those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He uploaded it to ajin.net
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishi-sensei... And even minister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatter has demanded two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First was for the government to admit \Nthe experiments on demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and to reveal the profit made of those experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And second, to recognize the rights of demi-humans in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bull! No one is going to accept such demands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's why you must stop Sato\N before he gets to the minister. At any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your last chance, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As I see it, stating demands to humans while hiding inside society\N is a cowardly act that should be responded to adequately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are not going to fulfill the demands that Sato made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Statements that some kind of researches on demi-humans \Nare being carried out, do not reflect the reality at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The government isn't going to submit\Nto this kind of demands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to send forces to quickly\Nresolve this conflict instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These statements were made by the press secretary \N of the cabinet at the conference two days ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The government is preparing to take extreme measures\Nafter demi-human Sato declared the second wave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are also looking for any information that\Ncan help to find him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore them. Act normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell most teens apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Most teens my age are acting exactly the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagai! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a bigger idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Got some kind of towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We are showing you Sato and other demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you encounter them, then immediately report to police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it the guy sitting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We better call police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we aren't running away anymore. \NWhat's next? Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo?..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've stayed with old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the decision yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go straight to Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really a moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, right now we don't stand a chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we locate his hideout. Then what?\N What two teens could possibly do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to stop him? Trap in the cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we going to do with it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can't do anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have only two cards on our hands that we can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First is me. I'm smarter than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have tranquilizer guns and we have\Nno place to contain ajins, so we must improvise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I once told you that I can leave you disabled \Nfor the rest of your life. Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For example. Not far from the village\N there was a dried up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Point is, there was no air inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Soil bacteria consumed all the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And if a human enters space without oxygen,\N then he'll immediately lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And ajin will keep losing it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Second card is that we already have\Nskills most suitable for the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of these three skill would \Nyou like have on the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First - strong body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Second - strategical thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Third one - immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong body of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Anyone would choose immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have considerably more possibilities to fight with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sato-san has way more\Nresources, people and experience than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us fighting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we going to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll search for an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And he must be influential enough\Nto provide us with considerable support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you speeding up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we looking for an ally? I have one on my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then explain it at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn it, not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he's going to conceal them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool you are. There's not a chance\Nhe's going to leave them in the same spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only were you driving like crazy, but you also\N  took us to the former Sato base! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally! Took it long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After I've been found out, I ordered an investigation \Nat the detective agency to find some information
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about demi-human research department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they found some quite interesting guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment searches are also going in other\Nprefectures, such as Kanagawa, Chiba and Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't found any leads to Sato yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also sent guards to the young surgeon\N that tops the list as a preventive measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Police units have been ordered to be on a stand-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Tosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm dead then your miserable life will end as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, Nakano! He's quite an interesting guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's loved one is in coma and he's paying all the expanses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly can't make this much money at the usual job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a reason to stop Sato\Nand hang onto this seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And even better! His loved one is his weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The board meeting is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned demi-humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit smoking tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to be with you as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never lose that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Shimomura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the tv.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Where did you get my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn on the tv. Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What we are witnessing is the police chasing the stolen car!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our sources say that demi-human,\N Nagai Kei, is in the driver's seat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai Kei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where we are heading to, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn battery gone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Police asks citizens to free the road to avoid unnecessary accidents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the road to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Driver and his accomplice are heading toward central Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch to the headphones and use fake IDs.\N I'm going through the back entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminals are inside the hospital! Am sending the men in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover both main and back entrances!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to be of service!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait outside. We are going in by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad, Nagai?!\N What are you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Explanations later! Hide somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever! If they'll try to take me\N by force then stop them with the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost?! Are you talking about that black monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a funny joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead serious! It scared the hell out\N of me when it first appeared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, hide! You'll only get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Nagai is somehow\Nconnected to Sato after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what's your job is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My job...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have no future if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight on! Fight for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tension is hanging in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Police surrounded the building and started hospital evacuation,\Nexpecting some kind of terrorist act from demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to never see your face again, Tosaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad, because we'll be seeing\N each other quite often. Through the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not rush thing. All I want is to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not talk outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather is truly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to catch me then I'll summon my ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my orders he goes nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll give you hell of a time even\Nif you manage to put me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape easily this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't get away as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai! What are you doing this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere, Nakano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the orders? To shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...is doing the opposite of what I order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to achieve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Class room is filled with evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Drops of sweat are leaving traces on the text book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Life was quite and boring, but stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This was never meant to happen. And to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It all happened because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't us who turned out lives into complete nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm going to believe demi-humans word!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen! I don't really get all that stuff, but I can say one thing. \NWe're definitely going to deal with Sato! Whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And for her as well! So please, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll become your pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your immortal soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspect captured. We're going to deal with him from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it truly Nagai Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Just a lookalike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It came to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Glad to meet you again. Sato is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, government\Ndidn't agree with our demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I decided to start with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...the young and perspective surgeon.\NSpecialist with a great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:22:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As the second wave progresses,\Nwe are going to prepare for the third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And third wave will be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take over this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you see my dream as an absurd one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.18,0:24:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Done from russkie subs special for anon.\NHope someone actually knowing shit picks up the releases.
